General.Name: Akelius Residential Property AB (publ)
General.Description: Akelius Residential Property AB (publ) owns, manages, rents, restores, and upgrades residential properties. The company owns 20 thousand rental apartments in the metropolitan cities New York, Boston, Washington D.C., Austin, Montreal, Toronto, Ottawa, Quebec City, London, and Paris. The company was incorporated in 1971 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden. Akelius Residential Property AB (publ) is a subsidiary of Akelius Apartments Ltd.
